T02D3389:56a-1: si t'a ta pa tree n'a ma aa pa r'a dzi t'a s'a dha nam /
T02D3389:56a-3: gzhan gyis mi thub pa gdugs dkar mo zhes bya ba'i sgrub thabs /
T02D3389:56a-4: 'phags ma gdugs dkar mo can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3389:56a-5: sngon du bstan pa'i cho gas rang gi snying gar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la /
T02D3389:56a-6: aom gyi sa bon dkar po las yongs su rdzogs
T02D3389:56a-7: pa'i gzhan gyis mi thub pa gdugs dkar mo can
T02D3389:56a-8: zhes bya ba zhal gsum pa /
T02D3389:56a-10: zhal so so la spyan gsum gsum mo //
T02D3389:56a-11: yan lag thams cad dang rtsa ba'i zhal ni dkar po'o //
T02D3389:56a-12: sngon po dang dmar po ni g-yon pa dang g-yas kyi zhal lo //
T02D3389:56a-13: 'khor lo dang lcags kyu dang gzhu ni g-yas kyi phyag na'o //
T02D3389:56a-14: rdo rje dkar po dang mda' dang /
T02D3389:56a-15: zhags pa dang bcas pa'i sdigs mdzub ni g-yon gyi phyag na'o //
T02D3389:56a-16: khro po'i lta stangs dang bcas pas gza' thams cad 'joms par byed ma /
T02D3389:56a-17: lha rdzas kyi rgyan dang na bzas rnam par brgyan ma /
T02D3389:56a-18: rnam par snang mdzad spyi bor gnas par bsams la /
T02D3389:56a-20: de la g-yas pa'i lag pa'i khu tshur dang /
T02D3389:56a-21: sdigs mdzub ni snying gar yang dag par bzhag la /
T02D3389:56a-22: g-yon pa'i lag pa rdo rje khu tshur steng du 'phyar ba'o //
T02D3389:56a-24: aom s'i t'a ta pa tre /
T02D3389:56a-26: sarba gra ha aa nu tr'a sha ya tr'a sha ya /
T02D3389:56a-28: drum drum h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a zhes bya'o //
T02D3389:56a-29: 'phags ma gzhan gyis mi thub pa zhes bya ba'i
T02D3389:56a-30: gdugs dkar mo can gyi sgrub pa'i thabs rdzogs so
T02D3389:56a-31: // pandi ta don yod rdo rje dang /
